{"tid":2201729,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何柱國父子兩公司 偷雞用星島地址  違工業邨用途 上月補鑊急改","createTime":"2020-09-14T04:30:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T05:37:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e3b5cceed421e8fe9e0750ee68b561caada181c8","tid":2201729,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T04:30:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200914/VHDDZJVVYBD2LL7GHCTGZZ5CWE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200914%2FVHDDZJVVYBD2LL7GHCTGZZ5CWE%2F&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8B4w7aMtX%2B%2FJ%2BUdoe8qorTI%3D&h=8f4d9675\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200914%2FVHDDZJVVYBD2LL7GHCTGZZ5CWE%2F&h=c9a095dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200914/VHDDZJVVYBD2LL7GHCTGZZ5CWE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n何柱國父子兩公司 偷雞用星島地址 <br />\n違工業邨用途 上月補鑊急改<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】近月積極處理賣盤的星島（1105）主席、全國政協常委何柱國，與兒子何正德疑涉違規使用工業園用地。本報偵查發現兩人經營多間私人公司中，最少兩間曾登記星島於將軍澳工業邨駿昌街七號的地址為註冊地址，與科技園地契用途相違背。兩公司更「巧合」地上月一同更改註冊地址，懷疑為「補鑊」。何正德現為科技園董事會成員。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：星島美資產多過內地<br />\n<br />\n何柱國在八間香港註冊公司擔任董事，大部份與家族煙草生意及報業有關。惟其中一間帝域（香港）有限公司並非經營報業，但註冊地址卻在屬科技園所有的將軍澳工業邨。公司疑似是炒賣物業的控股公司，2006年7月以1,980萬元購入柴灣嘉業街百樂門大廈3樓共5個單位，持貨近10年，2016年4月售予寶領有限公司，作價1.1億元，賬面淨賺9,020萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XfZjBAJAxnY_NnWOHHpiUWtM9oM=/913x847/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DD4734MUOJBNHNFA2NVEOHIDTQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXfZjBAJAxnY_NnWOHHpiUWtM9oM%3D%2F913x847%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDD4734MUOJBNHNFA2NVEOHIDTQ.jpg&h=4d24d91b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■何柱國與兒子何正德經營的私人公司中，至少兩間使用星島廠房作註冊地址。<br />\n<br />\n帝域今年提交的申報表提。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n帝域（香港）1997年成立，當年註。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n同屬星島執董的何正德，其初創。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ux24-16Rzt1ZkSur2_mKAsBr6IA=/1280x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HKQHIKCQ4JCO3A2NMPNHVP5BQI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fux24-16Rzt1ZkSur2_mKAsBr6IA%3D%2F1280x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHKQHIKCQ4JCO3A2NMPNHVP5BQI.jpg&h=fe263b0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■帝域（香港）上月申請遷至李寶椿大廈，現為一間會計師事務所。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3_NJR9SF9hzxem9ehv_9vcDCB6g=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KGXJUBH5LRHE5HNCWDVCWTFWPM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3_NJR9SF9hzxem9ehv_9vcDCB6g%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKGXJUBH5LRHE5HNCWDVCWTFWPM.jpg&h=b8f60806&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Spectrum 28上月1日入紙搬到尖沙嘴九龍中心，現址為利駿達會計師事務所。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n何：𠵱啲嘢我理㗎？<br />\n<br />\nSpectrum 28為何正德成立的離岸公司，。。。。<br />\n<br />\n何正德另一投資公司Bear Venture Limited，。。。。<br />\n<br />\n根據2007年星島與科技園的租賃協議，「。。。。<br />\n<br />\n本報曾致電何柱國查詢，對方得悉事件後表示：「𠵱啲我唔識，你問公司，我唔理𠵱啲，你問我多餘嘅。」記者再三追問下，他反問「𠵱啲嘢我理㗎？」後便掛線。<br />\n<br />\n科技園回應本報指根據巡查記綠，。。。。<br />\n<br />\n大律師陸偉雄指，。。。。"},{"pid":"24862aa9f1c759435e50bc7002fbc216638e4f94","tid":2201729,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T04:33:19.000Z","msg":"呢D先係詐騙"},{"pid":"e90f7e75770c94493f3acaeff2a99dc333d95412","tid":2201729,"uid":7369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T04:33:39.000Z","msg":"政協可以犯法架，基本法遲啲會加番上去架啦！"},{"pid":"3b1bd64932ae3a3922611e0e6ea92229f965f29f","tid":2201729,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T05:37:16.000Z","msg":"改返就唔洗負責？"}]}